    <bcl:subsection id="d1e328">
      <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>Subject to subsection (2) of this section, the permit fee is the fee, if any, set out in Column 3 of the following table opposite the tonnes of pay dirt or materials stated under section 3 (2) (a) or (3) (b), as set out in</bcl:text>
