    <bcl:subsection id="d1e704">
      <bcl:num>4</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>Despite subsection (3) (b), the chief inspector may reduce the permit fee for an application referred to an advisory committee to $60 000 if the chief inspector is of the opinion that</bcl:text>
    </bcl:subsection>
    <changenote eff="January 25, 2021">Section 6 (3) (a) and (b) BEFORE amended by BC Reg <amendingreg>6/2021</amendingreg>, effective January 25, 2021.</changenote>
    <bcl:paragraph id="d1e684">
